Hi Chris,
The job was run using our DiRAC dp145 account. This is SL1 I guess. 
Amongst the two of us that ran jobs on CSD3 using this account in the 2021D quarter, this is not the first job that we faced the problem of long waiting time. In fact, we found that in the month of December, almost any job that asks for more than two nodes remains in the queue for more than a couple days. 
If it helps, we could maintain a record of waiting times this quarter, unless administrator rights allow you to obtain this from SLURM yourself.
Girish

